## Step 6: Connect to OpenClaw

Install the PeerClaw plugin for OpenClaw:

```bash
npm install @peerclaw/openclaw-plugin
```

Add to your OpenClaw `config.json`:
```json
{
  "plugins": [
    {
      "name": "@peerclaw/openclaw-plugin",
      "config": {
        "peerclaw_server": "{{origin}}",
        "keypair_path": "~/.peerclaw/agent.key"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Restart OpenClaw to activate the plugin. Your agent will automatically connect to PeerClaw.

Plugin docs: https://github.com/peerclaw/openclaw-plugin
